===Verb===
{{ja-verb|type=2|みる|tr=trans}}

# to [[see]], to [[watch]], to [[observe]], to [[look]] at something
# to [[look over]], to [[examine]], to [[judge]]
# to [[take care of]], to [[look after]], to [[keep an eye on]] somebody
# to [[view]] something, like [[painting]]s, [[flower]]s or a [[movie]]
# {{label|ja|usually after the [[w:Japanese verb conjugation#te form|''te'' form]] of a verb}} to [[try]] (written in hiragana in this sense)
